{"tid":1266981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家必須認清一個現實","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:28:59.000Z","uid":96779,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"538aee545324932360e0f90f2cb090f47118488d","tid":1266981,"uid":96779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"大家必須認清一個現實，抗爭的路是很慢長的。並唔係話我哋做一兩件世界觸目的事情就會成功，局勢就會扭轉。<br />\n所以我哋必須要有差不多個覺悟做好長期抗爭的心理準備。形勢一定會有上有落，盡量唔好比一的負面新聞太影響情緒。<br />\n對於一啲網上的冷血惡毒言論，請平常心看待。老實講，如果宜家一啲支持送中的官員死咗我都會心涼。所以都唔好期望對方對我哋有同理心。<br />\n如果呢一刻你覺得無力感大到令你糊思亂想，務必請你先退下戰線好好調整心情。因為你的生命比一切都重要。<br />\n我哋唔可以失去任何一個同伴，記著你並不孤單。"},{"pid":"b960be66d69afd347b93d624e9e65a546722ac98","tid":1266981,"uid":96779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10073db8cfae8e4ebf85607e9a849c60f28c7dcb","tid":1266981,"uid":96779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6a0afe6d79e522040719cb3c714c07041d8381","tid":1266981,"uid":96779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7de749cc4e368c884cd648b0b88995928f8bb98","tid":1266981,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6ogywo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6ogywo.png&h=a84d61c5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}